{"tid":1509032,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"各位手足對唔住","createTime":"2019-08-26T16:49:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T14:49:13.000Z","uid":58516,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cdb8b2311238f037d659faf989a9027c5046d050","tid":1509032,"uid":58516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:49:19.000Z","msg":"嚟緊九月一我會去台灣一個星期<br />\n我知我呢個時間離開香港係衰仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n爭執咗好耐都係決定維持返個行程<br />\n不過都想做返啲嘢彌補下我愧疚嘅心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暫時諗住印啲文宣派下或者過膠搵地方貼下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個喼嘅位唔係好多位 有冇啲咩圖簡而精推介畀小弟<br />\n會喺高雄同墾丁附近 有冇啲咩搞作可以做同埋有咩地點可以介紹下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想帶支旗仔去但有咩地方可以插旗或者掛下 Banner<br />\n可能會掛啲文宣喺背囊周圍行<br />\n行程絕對可變 可行嘅嘢我都會嘗試去做<br />\n到時或者會喺度匯報一下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1132f6d668adf4a0cda2841f08436ce24433613e","tid":1509032,"uid":58516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:49:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67819ced5e5f98116e32811c72e421b11bf1208d","tid":1509032,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:50:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">求幫推</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最新post 睇得清楚d + 加左明天有義士再審係頂！</span></span>(極正經)(請推至長期置頂)被捕義士進程，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b34bbb31224a3a8ee56cc85f340275a26aca861d","tid